<HiddenText ID="x64634" Name="How is GPA calculated?"><showText type="boolean" label="Enable to feature this question." readonly="false" required="false" hidden="false">true</showText><OpenningText type="string" label="Question Text" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">How is GPA calculated?</OpenningText><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Answer Text" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<p>Your grade point average (GPA) is calculated by dividing the total amount of grade points earned by the total amount of credit hours attempted. Your grade point average may range from 0.0 to a 4.0.</p>
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 345px;"><colgroup><col style="mso-width-source: userset; mso-width-alt: 6186; width: 145pt;" width="145" /> <col span="2" style="width: 65pt;" width="65" /> <col style="mso-width-source: userset; mso-width-alt: 2986; width: 70pt;" width="70" /> </colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr class="rust_txt" style="height: 15.0pt;">
<td class="xl63" colspan="4" style="border-right-width: 0.5pt; height: 15px; width: 345px; text-align: center; background-color: #d4d4d4;"><strong>Example</strong></td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 15.0pt;">
<td class="xl67" height="15" style="height: 15.0pt; border-top: none;">Course</td>
<td class="xl67" style="border-top: none; border-left: none;">Credit Hours</td>
<td class="xl67" style="border-top: none; border-left: none;">Grade</td>
<td class="xl67" style="border-top: none; border-left: none;">Grade Points</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 15.0pt;">
<td class="xl66" height="15" style="height: 15.0pt;">GS 120 Pathway Life Skills</td>
<td class="xl71" style="border-top: medium none; text-align: center;">3</td>
<td class="xl71" style="border-top: medium none; border-left: medium none; text-align: center;">B-</td>
<td class="xl72">8.1 (3&times;2.7)</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 15.0pt;">
<td class="xl66" height="15" style="height: 15.0pt;">FDREL 121 Book of Mormon</td>
<td class="xl73" style="text-align: center;">2</td>
<td class="xl73" style="border-left: medium none; text-align: center;">B+</td>
<td class="xl72">6.8 (2&times;3.4)</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 15.0pt;">
<td class="xl63" colspan="2" style="border-right-width: 0.5pt; height: 15px; background-color: #d4d4d4; text-align: center;"><strong>Total Credit Hours 5</strong></td>
<td class="xl63" colspan="2" style="border-right-width: 0.5pt; height: 15px; background-color: #d4d4d4; text-align: center;"><strong>Total GradePoints 14.9</strong></td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 15.0pt;">
<td class="xl68" colspan="4" style="height: 15pt; text-align: center;">GPA = Total Grade Points &divide; Total Credit Hours Attempted</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 15.0pt;">
<td class="xl63" colspan="4" style="height: 15pt; text-align: center;">2.98 GPA = 14.9 &divide; 5</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>The following chart lists the point values per credit hour.</p>
